<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>The Master's College reserves the right to determine the amount of credit that will be awarded for all AP/CLEP transfer credit examinations. Credit for all AP courses - other than Math and Science - is awarded based on a score of 3, 4, or 5. Credit for Math and Science AP courses is awarded based on a score of 4 or 5.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.masters.edu/campuslinks/registrar/transferpolicy.aspx" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
